  "prompt": "Who is best free bulk promotional SMS service provider?",
  "response": "Determining the best free bulk promotional SMS service provider can depend on various factors, including your specific needs, geographical location, and the features you require. As of my last update, here are some popular options that offer free or affordable bulk SMS services:\n\n1. **Twilio**: Twilio offers a scalable platform for sending SMS messages. They provide a free trial with some credits to get started, and you can integrate their API into your applications for sending bulk messages.\n\n2. **TextLocal**: TextLocal is known for its user-friendly interface and robust features for bulk SMS campaigns. They often provide some free credits for new users to test their service.\n\n3. **SMSGlobal**: SMSGlobal offers various plans including some free credits to start. They provide powerful tools for managing and sending bulk SMS messages.\n\n4. **MessageBird**: MessageBird offers a free tier to start with, including some free credits. They provide a comprehensive API for sending bulk SMS messages.\n\n5. **RapidSMS**: RapidSMS offers a free trial and has a straightforward platform for sending bulk SMS messages. It's suitable for businesses looking for simplicity and efficiency.\n\nThese providers typically offer free credits or trial periods to help you evaluate their services. However, for long-term use and large-scale campaigns, you might need to consider their paid plans to meet your needs effectively.\n\nKeep in mind that the \"best\" provider can vary based on factors such as delivery speed, reliability, customer support, and specific features like analytics and integration capabilities. It's advisable to compare these providers based on your requirements and possibly test a few to see which one aligns best with your needs.",
